    <p>
      Running those four combinations gives you roughly 127 grams of protein across the day — right in the target range for most men over 50, with a total active preparation time of about 10 minutes.
    </p>

    <p>
These foods make it much easier to follow a simple approach like the
<a href="/blog/30-gram-protein-rule/">30-gram protein rule</a>, where you aim for roughly 25–30 grams per meal.
</p>

    <div class="killer-line">
      You don't need a meal plan.<br />You need a short list of foods you actually eat.
